thread.title: BRIEF-Jui Li Enterprise says new share prices and updates issuance of convertible corporate bonds

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Jui Li Enterprise says new share prices and updates issuance of convertible corporate bonds

organizations.name: reuters) - jui li enterprise co ltd

text:
Feb 26 (Reuters) - Jui Li Enterprise Co Ltd
* Says it plans to issue up to 40 million shares at the price of T$9.12 per share via private placement, or issue unsecured convertible corporate bonds worth T$120 million with a term of three years and coupon rate of 6 percent
* The proceeds will be used for working capital and loan repayment
